Quote:  there are vigorous <i>Slanging Contests</i> in which the contestants try to outdo each other by using phrases like the following: `You're up the shoot.' `Oh, bullswool.' `Go jump in the lake'. .... `Shivery dick'. `Shiver me timbers.' ... `Like smoke in a wheelbarrow.' ... `Mole balls to you.' ... `Go and have a roll.'
